recipes.name: Grilled Sea Bass
recipes.directions: 1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat. 2. Brush sea bass with olive oil and season with salt and pepper. 3. Grill fish for 4-5 minutes per side, or until cooked through. 4. Serve with lemon wedges.

recipes.name: Summer Vegetable Pasta
recipes.directions: 1. Cook pasta according to package directions. 2. Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat. 3. Add garlic and cook for 1-2 minutes, or until fragrant. 4. Add zucchini, yellow squash, and tomatoes and cook for 5-7 minutes, or until vegetables are tender. 5. Toss pasta with vegetables and top with grated parmesan cheese.
